        {
            "id": 6011263,
            "title": "川普再度喊話鮑爾：直接降息1個百分點！",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國總統川普在勞工統計局 (BLS) 周五 (6 日) 公布 5 月非農就業報告後，連續在 Truth Social 發文，對聯準會 (Fed) 主席鮑爾施壓，呼籲立即降息，藉此壓低借貸成本並提振經濟。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011263%2Fl%2Fb873dea76dfe45a56504dfefc0854e22.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">川普再度喊話鮑爾：直接降息1個百分點！(圖：REUTERS/TPG)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普先在貼文中表示：「美國現在火熱！六個月前還冷得像冰塊！邊境已經關閉，物價下跌，工資上漲！」隨後，他批評 Fed 升息動作遲緩，直指：「聯準會的『慢郎中』(指鮑爾) 是場災難！歐洲已經降息 10 次了，我們一次都沒有。儘管如此，我們國家表現依然很好。直接降息 1 個百分點吧！這會是火箭燃料！」</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普最後強調，若 Fed 降息，美國即將到期的債務利率就能大幅下降。他寫道：「如果 Fed 的『慢郎中』能夠降息，那我們即將到期的長短期債務利率都能大幅下降。拜登大多發行短期公債。現在幾乎沒有通膨了 (再也沒有了)，但如果真的捲土重來，就升息對抗就行了。非常簡單！他讓我們國家損失了一大筆錢。借貸成本應該要大幅降低！」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img alt=\"圖：川普Truth Social\" data-height=\"660\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.9196969696969697\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6011263/m/55bff53db674da1d609cdfeae72a692a.jpg\" data-width=\"607\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6011263/l/55bff53db674da1d609cdfeae72a692a.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption>圖：川普 Truth Social</figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外界認為，川普此舉凸顯其對聯準會貨幣政策持續不滿，也反映其將利率政策作為重要經濟工具，以因應潛在的經濟放緩風險。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>持續更新...</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
